{"type": "article", "id": 2883, "title": "Nendo组合式办公家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-16T07:54:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232320nbJUzlHOF354Du0W.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t传统的办公家具用品被日本设计事务所 Nendo 赋予了新的定义方式，日前，他们为日本办公用品品牌 KOKUYO 带来了一系列可以任意组合的家具产品，运用哑光黑铁材质，将办公桌、办公椅、置物架等基础办公家具通过不同的形式组合在一起，创造了多个丰富多元的办公环境，置物架将不仅仅承担收纳的功能，延伸的部分就可以成为办公桌，置物架的内部甚至可以放入一把办公椅，成为一个小型办公空间。这一系列的办公产品将亮相本月 21 日开幕的科隆国际办公家具展。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232317CMrNUaxVdzvRutYy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232318K48Xz6CShlOuUstT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232318JD20vhcWRtFXa4ml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232319syS0QLADNUXT7vo3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232319BhKJLWY98irFj0v7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}